應用程式的Android虛擬裝置，從未登入順豐或創建順豐帳戶的情況下，仍然可以在「最近使用」的列表上，看到不少位於香港及台灣的用戶姓名、地址及電話。而這些聯絡資料，與測試用的裝置完全無關，很大可能是由於應用程式的保安漏洞，將不屬於「未登入用戶」的「最近使用記錄」顯示出來。 鄭松泰表示，會要求私隱專員主動跟進相關問題，以保障市民的私隱。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-19-2020/60178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-19-2020%2F60178&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5AsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=f464cb44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-19-2020/60178</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2020<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013080a606583a47cfee57f0c8d0c23681d39338","tid":1887524,"uid":29689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"消防啱唔啱例丫<br />\n有冇花曬頭cover 唔到？<br />\n係咪又諗住知法犯法？"},{"pid":"6a90b46e872a4641f58c9c2cab126f1a56c08f0f","tid":1887524,"uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/87045769_1062287280795346_1588694414081916928_n.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_ohc=cfhjSWAbUxoAX_j329J&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-2.fna&amp;oh=594f80a7ee484982c53384b9d13116dd&amp;oe=5EBC0A4A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F87045769_1062287280795346_1588694414081916928_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_ohc%3DcfhjSWAbUxoAX_j329J%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-2.fna%26oh%3D594f80a7ee484982c53384b9d13116dd%26oe%3D5EBC0A4A&h=082e2901&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1792a88c46b7e273e5049db2f828fce5100c2461","tid":1887524,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b9bfeb0fd8a4a22782c8283aeffc89860fbdc55","tid":1887524,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T15:05:20.000Z","msg":"鄭錦滿<br />\n昨天 14:48 發佈 &middot; <br />\n今日再就「暴動罪」到北角警署續保，差佬喺報案室加設咗封到頂嘅巨型透明屏障，要開個氣窗仔先交到張身份證，防護設備仲高規格過醫院。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net